{"tid":1838514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"病毒襲港 人人自危 要立即罷工罷課","createTime":"2020-01-24T05:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T12:01:29.000Z","uid":36111,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c1f5e59e0a403a326029fb1d32614867a5d3aefb","tid":1838514,"uid":36111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:00:52.000Z","msg":"依家病毒打到嚟，香港政府唔封關<br />\n支那人大舉入侵，香港九龍新界冇得避。<br />\n唔想死就要抗爭。<br />\n醫護界罷工抗爭要支持，無可能由政府唔解決嘅問題造一班悲劇英雄出嚟。香港唔再需要悲劇英雄，屌你老母港共臭化閪。<br />\n<br />\n學生都要罷課，特別講緊係大專院校，有幾撚多支那仔女讀緊。對上一個sem 停課太耐，佢地返咗支那幾耐、去咗邊到根本冇人人知，喺hall 喺campus 見到唔戴口罩嘅基本都係講普通話。繼續返學、困喺間細細嘅課室隨時命都保唔住。仲未講新年之後嘅大規模人口移動，所以放完新年假返學大家都係兇多吉少。<br />\n<br />\n同時，成件事都顯示咗主權問題嘅重要性。香港獨立成為主權國家，保住你條命、保住你個關口。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要保命就罷工罷課</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港獨立，唯一出路</span></span>"},{"pid":"c6a7479ff6e30e64292bf4d701c5cb230ad079d3","tid":1838514,"uid":343361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:03:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放假啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"1b4ab29a337ef54c034cae6793c6e3c83074e85f","tid":1838514,"uid":36111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0613b0bc159b5cc98c2b50d66069224bf29d5813","tid":1838514,"uid":36111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4446526f6dcc6eb175cce7629f81e5dc4f82c2f","tid":1838514,"uid":81449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656c18ece33273d6601156fce2e5f6bb4b50fa44","tid":1838514,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"係hall一定仆街"},{"